item.title: By: Suzi
item.dc:creator: Suzi
item.description:
In reply to <a href="/birchbox-swap-party/#comment-406">Sarah Cosper</a>.
I'm pretty new to it, but I'm currently awaiting a mini Urban Decay Revolution in 69 ($7 shipped) and a full size bottle of Primer Potion ($10 shipped!). I've also made three successful sales so far of deluxe sample size stuff I wasn't using and netted almost $30...so more money for more makeup! The mods update usernames with that little title next to it (White Level 1, or whatever) to indicate how many successful swaps someone has had, and they have a banned user list to try and keep people honest. It just seemed like such a cool idea when I heard about it, and people have some pretty impressive swap lists. The only hard part is not losing your mind and buying all the things.
